<item>
            <title>[LU-12364] idle disconnect shouldn&apos;t set IDLE going to reconnect</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12364</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ptlrpc_disconnect_idle_interpret() sets IDLE state but can change that to CONNECTING in few cycles if any one has been interested in reconnection yet.&lt;br/&gt;
these few cycles can be hit with ptlrpc_set_add_req() check that the connection is not idling.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
